<div class="container">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <h1>Welcome to Blocipedia</h1>
    <h2 class="description">Blocipedia is a great way to collaborate on community-sourced content.  </br> Make wikis for fun or for work.<br /> This app lets you create and share wikis publicly or privately <br /> with other collaborators of your choice.</h2>

    <br />
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Create as many wikis as you like!</h3>
          <%= link_to "Free Plan", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Upgrade to the Premium Plan to create private wikis</h3>
          <%= link_to "Premium Plan", new_charge_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      </div>
    </div> <!-- close "row" -->
  </div>
</div>
